			<td><b>Senior Fellow and Director of Education,&nbsp;THX, Ltd.</b></td>
		</tr>
		
		
		
			<td><br>Dahl began his audio career in retail sales while studying at university.  More than 20 years later, his career has spanned numerous home theater, cinema and professional studio projects.  As Director of Education at THX, Dahl spearheads the THX Certified Dealer Technician program, which serves thousands of professional home theater dealers and installers around the world. Prior to joining THX, he was an independent consultant to the consumer electronics industry, working with clients such as Atlantic Technology, DWIN and Soundstream. Today, he is a Top Ten CEDIA Instructor, and holds training courses and seminars at CEA events.</td>
